Class AbstractUncertainObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • elki.data.uncertain.AbstractUncertainObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    SimpleGaussianContinuousUncertainObject, UniformContinuousUncertainObject, UnweightedDiscreteUncertainObject, WeightedDiscreteUncertainObject
    public abstract class AbstractUncertainObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements UncertainObject
    Abstract base implementation for UncertainObjects, providing shared functionality such as bounding box access and random generation.
